description: Submission of a Sustainable Waste Strategy for Block 5 only pursuant to Condition 41 of planning permission 2019/0024 dated 29 January 2021.
decision_conditions: Condition : 1 - INFORMATIVE: The applicant is advised that Waste Collectors must be able to gain access to the refuse stores freely or by using an FB2 or FB4 standard pattern key in accordance with Wandsworth Supplementary Planning Document "Refuse and Recyclables 2014".

Condition : 2 - INFORMATIVE: You are advised that this permission constitutes approval of a Sustainable Waste Strategy pursuant to Condition 41 in relation to Block 5 (Phase 1 of the approved 'Detailed Element Phasing') only. Information for the remaining blocks/phases will be required to be submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority in accordance with the requirements of Condition 41 of planning permission 2019/0024 dated 29/01/2021.
application_type_full: Approval of details reserved by a condition (discharge)
